802
00:57:53,316 --> 00:57:54,436
We roll him.

803
00:58:27,996 --> 00:58:29,076
Jimmy.

804
00:58:29,116 --> 00:58:31,356
You don't know
what a relief it's...

805
00:58:32,396 --> 00:58:33,636
What's this?

806
00:58:34,956 --> 00:58:36,436
You don't know this guy?

807
00:58:38,436 --> 00:58:40,196
I do not.

808
00:58:43,116 --> 00:58:45,156
Why don't you
have a closer look?

809
00:58:46,796 --> 00:58:48,316
I've never seen him in my life.

810
00:58:48,396 --> 00:58:50,716
-Hey!
