837
01:00:07,536 --> 01:00:09,296
Look, come on.

838
01:00:09,336 --> 01:00:11,096
You sent that guy for me
last night...

839
01:00:11,136 --> 01:00:12,816
tried to have me killed...

840
01:00:12,856 --> 01:00:13,976
and now you're feeding me...

841
01:00:14,016 --> 01:00:15,096
some bullshit story...

842
01:00:15,136 --> 01:00:16,576
about how Marvin's disappeared.

843
01:00:16,616 --> 01:00:17,736
He's been abducted.

844
01:00:17,776 --> 01:00:19,336
