845
01:00:19,376 --> 01:00:22,016
You know Marvin and l
would do nothing to harm you.

846
01:00:22,056 --> 01:00:23,736
You're like a son to him.

847
01:00:23,776 --> 01:00:26,136
He asked me to look after you.

848
01:00:26,176 --> 01:00:27,576
